<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3489379">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3489379/" class="title-link">不一样的世界史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3489379"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zxl/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1130001-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zxl/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">TickMark</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-07-31"
      class="main-meta">2010-07-31 17:46:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3489379_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  若干年前基于一个书评，便把商务版《罗马帝国衰亡史》购买了。但当我兴趣盎然欲尽一扫而光的畅快之意之时，却发现读不下去，因为我根本就缺乏对罗马帝国了解的最起码的基础知识。我本想在十分悠闲的情况下心平气和强行读完，也告失败。千里之行始于足下啊，我还没进化到那个阶...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3489379/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3489379_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3489379_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










